WEBVTT

00:00.329 --> 00:01.329
<i>Previously on "Heartland"...</i>

00:01.388 --> 00:02.989
Um, he ordered
the Saskatoon Berry.

00:03.056 --> 00:04.723
Most of our customers
prefer apple.

00:04.791 --> 00:05.724
The boy, Shane.

00:05.792 --> 00:06.725
Yeah.

00:06.793 --> 00:08.361
He's my son.

00:08.428 --> 00:10.262
What the hell am I gonna do?

00:10.330 --> 00:11.597
You don't repeat the past.

00:11.664 --> 00:13.466
I just need you to know
I'm behind Ashley,

00:13.533 --> 00:14.733
all the way.

00:14.834 --> 00:16.102
In fact,
I'm moving to BC with her.

00:16.169 --> 00:17.335
You're going with her?

00:17.403 --> 00:18.803
Okay...

00:18.871 --> 00:20.205
- Get 'er done.
- Absolutely.

00:22.375 --> 00:23.541
Shane?!

00:23.609 --> 00:24.675
Miranda?!

00:27.279 --> 00:28.213
What're you doing here?

00:28.280 --> 00:29.481
She's in full out labour.

00:29.548 --> 00:30.548
We never would've made it
to the hospital.

00:30.616 --> 00:32.317
It's a girl, Lou.
It's...

00:32.384 --> 00:34.118
<i>She's beautiful.</i>

